                          <span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:normal;font-style:normal">Ausstattung gemäß Arbeitsstättenverordnung</span>
                        </p>
                        <p/>
                        <p>
                          <span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:normal;font-style:normal">1 Toilette</span>
                        </p>
                        <p>
                          <span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:normal;font-style:normal">1 Urinalbecken</span>
                        </p>
                        <p>
                          <span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:normal;font-style:normal">1 Waschbecken</span>
                        </p>
                        <p>
                          <span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:normal;font-style:normal">1 Seifenspender</span>
                        </p>
                        <p>
                          <span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:normal;font-style:normal">1 Papierhandtuchspender</span>
                        </p>
                        <p>
                          <span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:normal;font-style:normal">1 Heizung und Beleuchtung mit Anschluss</span>
                          <br/>
                          <span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:normal;font-style:normal">   und Anschlussverlängerung.</span>
                        </p>
                        <p>
                          <br/>
                          <span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:normal;font-style:normal">Strom: 230 V / 16 A</span>
                          <br/>
                          <span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:normal;font-style:normal">Frischwasser: 3/4&#x22; GEKA-Kupplung</span>
                          <br/>
                          <span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:normal;font-style:normal">Abwasser: HT-Rohr NW 100</span>
