                              <span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:normal;font-style:normal">Kleinstmengen werden nicht gesondert vergütet</span>
                              <br/>
                              <br/>
                              <span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:normal;font-style:normal">Aufmaß nach verbrauchter Trockenmasse.</span>
